title: Super Dinosaur
overview: Leaping from the pages of the Skybound/Image comic book series by Robert Kirkman and Jason Howard, 'Super Dinosaur' stars 10 year old Derek Dynamo and his best-friend Super Dinosaur, a genetically engineered T-Rex with human-level intelligence and an aptitude for awesome combat gear. The fate of the world rests on the shoulders of the dynamic duo as the team up for epic crime-fighting adventures.
